				<td colspan="2"><span>Try this:
<br />
Play /Melody 1 2 3 4
<br />
Then start playing the first song (1) in your lineup solo....
<br />

<br />
Woohoo!  Melody starts again anyway!
<br />

<br />
So now if you want to play Manasong during down time, you have to start playing it, stop it, and start it again to keep it from going into Melody.  I'll be sending this in as a bug once servers are back up.  Would be nice if more in the bard community do the same.
<br />

<br />
Also not sure of this, but when I /melody during a raid, higher lag seems to make melody go to the next song a little too early, and a song gets dropped.  Anyone else seeing this?</span></td>
