				<td colspan="2"><span><blockquote><b>Quote:</b><br><span class="quote">Hello
<br />

<br />
This morning I became aware of some issues related to /melody and have already changed the code to correct it to the intended behavior.
<br />
In a couple of places in the code, /melody was not getting reset when it should have and was causing the melody to start up again. 
<br />

<br />
Here are the specifics:
<br />

<br />
* /stopsong now stops melody song.
<br />

<br />
* Singing via spell gem or /cast after using a /melody or during the playback of a /melody no longer transitions the song into the melody.
<br />

<br />

<br />
The changes will be put on Live servers when we do our next update, but I don't expect an emergency patch for this.
<br />

<br />
Cheers, 
<br />

<br />
---------------------------
<br />

<br />
Eric Cosky - &quot;Grumbuk&quot;
<br />

<br />
Assistant Lead Programmer, EverQuest
<br />

<br />
Sony Online Entertainment</span></blockquote>
<br />

<br />
So it'll be broken until Januaryish.
<br />

<br />
Kula</span></td>
