				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: WOO!!  Bards a Broke (Again)<a name="72119"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Jan 17 05 3:31 AM</span></td>
